flowchart TD
    subgraph Vulnerable Code Path
        A[User input: username field\nValue: admin or 1 equals 1 --] --> B[App concatenates input\ninto SQL string directly]
        B --> C["Resulting query:\nSELECT * FROM users\nWHERE username = 'admin' OR 1=1 --'"]
        C --> D[Database executes\nmanipulated query]
        D --> E[1=1 always true\nReturns all users]
        E --> F[Attacker bypasses login\nor dumps entire table]
    end

    subgraph Secure Code Path
        G[User input: username field\nValue: admin or 1 equals 1 --] --> H[App uses parameterized query\nSELECT * FROM users WHERE username = ?]
        H --> I[Input passed as\nbind parameter not SQL]
        I --> J[Database treats input\nas literal string data]
        J --> K[Query finds no user\nnamed that exact string]
        K --> L[Login fails safely\nNo injection possible]
    end
